HB 1165 Original 2026 Regular Session Deshotel
Abstract: Eliminates the city court judges in Marksville and Bunkie and provides for an
additional judge in the 12th JDC in Avoyelles Parish.
Present law provides for two judicial district court judges in the 12th JDC located in
Avoyelles Parish.
Proposed law retains present law but provides for an additional judgeship in the 12th JDC
located in Avoyelles Parish.
